      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, which remains in an impeccable state of preservation. Meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment, the exterior finish retains its original factory luster, while the interior remains devoid of any signs of occupancy. This specimen represents the pinnacle of its class, offering a showroom-quality experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our most rigorous standards of excellence.",
