    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like a total dream. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been loved and kept in tip-top shape, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
