    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute time capsule, meticulously maintained to a standard rarely seen outside of a museum. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero stone chips or swirl marks, having been professionally ceramic coated and strictly garage-kept. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather bolsters show no signs of compression or wear, and the original floor mats are pristine. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with the tactile precision of a new car. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, accompanied by a folder of exhaustive service records and both original keys. This is a non-smoker, no-pet vehicle that has never seen inclement weather. For the discerning buyer who refuses to settle for anything less than perfection, this is the definitive example.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
